title: BIP 65: Dogfooding Revenue into Setts
body:
TL;DR:
The BIP 65 proposal linked below has reached quorum with all three portions of the vote receiving overwhelming approval.

The team will take action to deploy these assets as soon as possible, blacklist the funds for native returns, and get in a regular cadence of depositing new revenues.

The proposal also gives the team the discretions to reallocate between setts and dogfood future revenues.

See the proposal here:
https://forum.badger.finance/t/bip-65-dogfooding-deposit-collected-fees-into-setts-blacklist-the-funds-for-native-returns/4853

Do you approve of the BIP being implemented as it stands?
author: 0xD1e5bE16a4f1EfE5ad21cC0F0c73FB8Ea8D1edCe
